query:
SELECT 
  td.id,
  td.taskId,
  t1.name as task_name,
  td.dependsOnTaskId,
  t2.name as depends_on_name,
  td.dependencyType
FROM task_dependencies td
JOIN tasks t1 ON td.taskId = t1.id
JOIN tasks t2 ON td.dependsOnTaskId = t2.id
WHERE (t1.name LIKE '%Einkaufen%' OR t2.name LIKE '%Einkaufen%'
   OR t1.name LIKE '%Suppe%' OR t2.name LIKE '%Suppe%')
ORDER BY td.id
